Requirements:

You must use:
1 server
1 web server (Nginx)
1 application server
1 application files (your code base)
1 database (MySQL)
1 domain name foobar.com configured with a www record that points to your server IP 8.8.8.8

Visual Representation:
https://miro.com/app/board/uXjVPd1XQBU=/

A server is a software or hardware computer that provides internet or function to other devices.The device is called clients.

Domain is the DNS. IT translate domain names into Ip address that initiating client.

The apache HTTP server is the type of www record that is in www.foobar.com.
The apache software foundation install all the oparation system.

Application server run process power and memory memory to run demanding application and it also provides the enviroment to run specific applications.

The web server it uses HTTP and other protocols to respond to client request made over the WWW.
It store the processing and deliver webpages to users.

The database it give access to creation,updating and retrieval of records.
It provides access to only users who have password.

The server uses internet to or DNS to communicate
